header: ['Turkish competition board launches probe into Audi, Porsche, VW, Mercedes-Benz and BMW']
article content: ['ISTANBUL (Reuters) - The Turkish Competition Board said on Wednesday that it launched an investigation into German carmakers Audi, Porsche, Volkswagen, Mercedes-Benz and BMW to determine whether they violated competition law. ', 'The competition board said findings regarding claims on the companies’ actions on security cooperation, environment cooperation and sharing competition-sensitive information were determined to be adequate to start an investigation. ', 'Reporting by Ebru Tuncay; Writing by Ezgi Erkoyun; Editing by Daren Butler']
